title: Episode 76: Gojee.com
description: This week on Let’s Eat In, Cathy is joined by Mike LaValle & Veronica Chan, founders of the personalized recipe-database website Gojee.com. Tune in to learn about how the site began and what Mike & Veronica would cook on a date meal! This episode was sponsored by HearstRanch.com.
author: info@heritageradionetwork.org (Heritage Radio Network)
